      "description": "Two-loop sunrise integral family in $D=2-2\\varepsilon$ with two massive and one massless propagator. Four UT master integrals: $I_1$ (double-tadpole), $I_2$ (sunrise with Kallen function normalization), $I_3$ and $I_4$ (sunrise with ISPs). One-to-one correspondence between 4 Schubert problems and 4 master integrals. 7 symbol letters (4 even + 3 odd, with $R_5+R_6+R_7=0$). Full $4 \\times 4$ canonical differential equation matrix derived. All letters reproduced as cross-ratios of Schubert solutions.",
